cs.SD, cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering): The paper presents a novel application of software defined radio (SDR) for speech signal processing.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper deals with the design of a radio receiver system for speech signals.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes an end-to-end learning approach using deep neural networks for speech signal detection and denoising.
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper deals with speech signal processing and denoising, which is a subfield of natural language processing.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a deep learning approach for speech signal processing, which falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence.
